&ANALYZE-SUSPEND _UIB-CODE-BLOCK _PROCEDURE Carga-Temporal V-table-Win 
PROCEDURE Carga-Temporal :
/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

EMPTY TEMP-TABLE PEDI.
IF NOT AVAILABLE Faccpedi THEN RETURN.

DEF VAR k AS INT NO-UNDO.
DO k = 1 TO NUM-ENTRIES(Faccpedi.nroref):
    FOR EACH B-DPEDI NO-LOCK WHERE B-DPEDI.codcia = Faccpedi.codcia
        AND B-DPEDI.coddoc = Faccpedi.codref
        AND B-DPEDI.nroped = ENTRY(k,Faccpedi.nroref):
        CREATE PEDI.
        BUFFER-COPY B-DPEDI TO PEDI.
    END.
END.

END PROCEDURE.

